I just made one inline comment in 015_quote_swift_credentials.py, but the same problem exists in several places. Basically some of the places where you replaced a call to locals() in formatting strings it needs to be replaced by a dictionary rather than just the var being formatted. It's correct in several locations but not others - I think the incorrect ones are mostly error messages or verbose logging that doesn't get touched by tests.
